#: ../../F/fnord.rst:12
msgid ""
"A word used in email and news postings to tag utterances as surrealist mind-"
"play or humor, esp. in connection with :ref:`Discordianism` and elaborate "
"conspiracy theories. \"I heard that David Koresh is sharing an apartment in "
"Argentina with Hitler. (Fnord.)\" \"Where can I fnord get the Principia "
"Discordia from?\""
msgstr ""
"メールやニュース投稿で、発言をシュルレアリスム的な心の遊びやユーモアとしてタグ付けするのに使われる語。特に\\ "
":ref:`Discordianism`\\ や手の込んだ陰謀論に関連して使われる。「David "
"KoreshがアルゼンチンでHitlerとアパートを共有していると聞いたよ。(Fnord.)」「Principia "
"Discordiaはどこでfnord手に入るんだ?」。"

#: ../../F/fnord.rst:19
msgid ""
"A :ref:`metasyntactic-variable`\\, commonly used by hackers with ties to "
":ref:`Discordianism` or the :ref:`Church-of-the-SubGenius`\\."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`Discordianism`\\ や\\ :ref:`Church-of-the-SubGenius`\\ "
"とのつながりを持つハッカーがよく使う\\ :ref:`metasyntactic-variable`\\ 。"
